            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "How much does delivery cost?",
            "content": "<p>Please note that <strong>free delivery </strong>for orders over £20 relates to Royal Mail 2nd Class delivery, UK residents only.</p><p>Delivery charges are specific to the country to which you would like your order delivered:</p><ul><li>UK – Next day delivery (note: this is next working day and must be ordered by 12:00) £5.95 / 1st class £3.95/ 2nd class £2.95</li><li>Europe – Royal Mail International Standard £8.95</li><li>Worldwide – Tracked Delivery – £10.95</li></ul><p>For US residents: Please note <strong>free delivery </strong>only applies to orders over $30 and is relevant for US residents only.</p><p>Usual postage costs are:</p><ul><li>1st Class – $3.95</li><li>Priority Mail – $8.95</li><li>Canada – $12.95</li><li>Worldwide – $14.95</li></ul>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_xnbxYN": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
