            "title": "How long will it take for my doddl order to arrive?",
            "content": "<p>It very much depends on where you are in the world, but as an approximate guide, if you have purchased from doddl.com:</p><p>UK is 1 to 5 days (depending on which postal service you selected at checkout), Europe is typically 1 to 2 weeks.</p><p>For customers who have purchased from our US doddl store delivery can take between 2-5 days</p><p>Rest of world from either of our stores is typically 2 to 4 weeks, but could be up to 6 weeks for certain countries.</p><p>Please contact team@doddl.com if you have any concerns about your doddl order.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_zFb4pr": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "What is the cut off for next day delivery?",
            "content": "<p>You must order by 12:00 Monday to Friday to guarantee next day delivery. Unfortunately we can't guarantee next day delivery for orders placed on Saturday or Sunday. Please note next day delivery option is only available for residents in the UK.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_UXjkpB": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "For international deliveries, who is responsible for import duties and taxes?",
            "content": "<p>You are responsible for covering the cost of any import duties and/or taxes that may apply to your specific country.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_znKzTU": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "There is a problem with my doddl order - what shall I do?",
            "content": "<p>We are very proud of the high quality of our products, however in the unusual situation there is a fault or your product has a defect, please e-mail us at team@doddl.com to let us know and we will investigate further to make sure you get the best possible doddl experience.</p>",
