        "item_LJYjcL": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "Do you offer any doddl discount codes?",
            "content": "<p>Not frequently, but we occasionally issue promo codes, most commonly providing 10% off for new customers. Please follow our main social media accounts <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/doddl\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">(Instagram</span></a>, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/doddlkids/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Facebook</span></a> and <a href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@doddlkids\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">TikTok</span></a>) or subscribe to our newsletter to be notified of any promotions..</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_6HxLhj": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "How do I use a doddl discount code at checkout?",
            "content": "<p>To redeem a code, simply:</p><ol><li>Add your items to the basket on doddl.com</li><li>Proceed to checkout</li><li>Enter your code in the “Promo code” or “Discount code” box</li><li>Click Apply, you’ll see confirmation of your savings or an error message if it's invalid.<a href=\"https://www.wethrift.com/doddl?utm_source=chatgpt.com\"> </a></li></ol>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_fQpVPa": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "Can I use more than one discount code on a single order?",
            "content": "<p>No, doddl's checkout system currently only allows one discount or promo code per order. Always enter the single code that gives you the best available savings.<br/><br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "item_r7zhzp": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
